## Linux Cheat Sheet
- pwd = shows current directory
- ls = lists files and folders
- cd = change directory
- ifconfig = shows network info and IP address
- ping = tests connection to a website
- netstat = shows active network connections
- traceroute = shows path data takes to reach destination
- nmap = scans a device for open ports

